leaving nowhere to return♪

00:16:47.480 --> 00:16:50.720
♪Borrow the endless cycles♪

00:16:51.280 --> 00:16:54.760
♪To fight for the most perfect outcome♪

00:16:55.520 --> 00:16:57.880
♪How to trace the threads
and follow cause and effect♪

00:16:57.880 --> 00:17:01.640
♪Seeking a strategy without flaw♪

00:17:01.920 --> 00:17:06.560
♪How to break free
from this fated yet unforeseen lock♪

00:17:06.720 --> 00:17:11.760
♪To live so as to shake the world♪

00:17:12.120 --> 00:17:16.240
♪With this journey,
I gain a fiercer edge♪

