♪I've planned
before I act countless times♪

00:17:18.520 --> 00:17:24.880
♪Fatal danger turned into a jest♪

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:29.200
♪Through this road,
I watch the endless rise and fall♪

00:17:29.240 --> 00:17:31.320
♪In the chapters lie ages
of decay and bloom♪

00:17:31.320 --> 00:17:33.240
♪Let us meet again♪

00:17:33.280 --> 00:17:38.440
♪One hurried path, and one at ease♪